{"TopicId":61270,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"The Reliant Robin Shuttle!","CreatedByName":"Starwhip","CreatedById":83990,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-27T12:22:46Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Starwhip","CreatedById":83990,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-27T12:22:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIf anyone watches the BBC America show, Top Gear, you\u0027ll know the Reliant Robin. And you may have even seen this thing. THIS is the most KSP-ish spacecraft I have EVER seen:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i41.tinypic.com/n4k5c1.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022n4k5c1.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe Reliant Robin Shuttle. You notice the solid fuel boosters, the liquid fuel tank, and, you know, the CAR on it...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i44.tinypic.com/1ie89z.jpg\u0022 alt=\u00221ie89z.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIgnition!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i44.tinypic.com/2l9s5kx.jpg\u0022 alt=\u00222l9s5kx.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELiftoff!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAnd, to top it off, a failure to separate the glider from the main rocket...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i43.tinypic.com/29diu00.jpg\u0022 alt=\u002229diu00.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWhich ended in a blaze of glory...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAll in all, a classic KSP moment. In real life.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Canopus","CreatedById":57774,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-27T13:37:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThey had an browser game about this which inspired a very early version of KSP too.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bsalis","CreatedById":32928,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-28T08:49:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThey almost pulled it off too.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EUnfortunately the Reliant Robin failed to decouple from the tank. Otherwise the RC pilot would have had a chance to land it.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tw1","CreatedById":59717,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-28T09:11:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHad a go of kerbalising that about a week ago\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tw1\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Tw1\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EPilot can\u0027t see... good start.\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/owcfCX8\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/owcfCX8.png\u0022 alt=\u0022owcfCX8.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/Zz0hnpS\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/Zz0hnpS.png\u0022 alt=\u0022Zz0hnpS.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/aK7jAyr\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/aK7jAyr.png\u0022 alt=\u0022aK7jAyr.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"astropapi1","CreatedById":57507,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-28T09:22:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHey, I\u0027M RELEVANT!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEDIT: Here\u0027s \u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.topgear.com/uk/games/rocket-robin\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ethe game\u003C/a\u003E they made about the darn thing.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bedwind","CreatedById":101903,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-28T15:12:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tw1\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Tw1\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EHad a go of kerbalising that about a week ago\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPOWAAAAAAAAH!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis is awesome.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tw1","CreatedById":59717,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-29T11:02:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022astropapi1\u0022 data-cite=\u0022astropapi1\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEDIT: Here\u0027s \u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.topgear.com/uk/games/rocket-robin\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ethe game\u003C/a\u003E they made about the darn thing.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThat\u0027s pretty cool.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/4YS2HFm\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/4YS2HFm.png\u0022 alt=\u00224YS2HFm.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOnce I worked out you could actually steer the thing, I managed to land too.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/6tsA8i9\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/6tsA8i9.png?1\u0022 alt=\u00226tsA8i9.png?1\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starwhip","CreatedById":83990,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-29T12:31:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOh, come on! My school internet blocks the game.... \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI wanna play it.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEDIT:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWAIT!!! IT WORKS!!!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEDIT2:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWhat was your altitude? 378,000 \u003Cem\u003Emeters?\u003C/em\u003E Jeez.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-01-29T12:55:55Z\u0022 title=\u002201/29/2014 12:55  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 29, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by Starwhip\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DisarmingBaton5","CreatedById":68576,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-29T22:35:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022astropapi1\u0022 data-cite=\u0022astropapi1\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EHere\u0027s \u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.topgear.com/uk/games/rocket-robin\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ethe game\u003C/a\u003E they made about the darn thing.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027m sorry, Kerbal Space Program. I have found my calling.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tw1\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Tw1\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EOnce I worked out you could actually steer the thing\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWhat? How?!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tw1","CreatedById":59717,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-30T04:20:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DisarmingBaton5\u0022 data-cite=\u0022DisarmingBaton5\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWhat? How?!\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EArrow keys once in flight.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThere\u0027s a bit of a trick to it, you\u0027ve got to turn to reduce your horizontal speed, or it will bounce and break.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Starwhip\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Starwhip\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWhat was your altitude? 378,000 \u003Cem\u003Emeters?\u003C/em\u003E Jeez.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYep! I managed to do about 410,000 one lucky time, but didn\u0027t manage to land. They don\u0027t really give units though. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThough it\u0027s probably a good thing they don\u0027t control the real one this way.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"technicalfool","CreatedById":70430,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-01T02:32:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ESmall factoid:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe cataclysmic explosion at the end was not the shuttle and rocket exploding. By the time the contraption hit the deck, it had expended all its fuel and went \u0022crunch\u0022 rather than \u0022bang\u0022.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHowever, this was an army bomb range, and the army were due to be dropping thousand-pounders in the location on that day. So, what you get in the video is a frame or two of the Robin embedding itself and wood splinters starting to poke out of the central \u0022fuel tank\u0022 (actually, just another set of SRBs in an orange container), and then a quick cut to a video of one of the thousand pound bombs going off in the same location.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOther than that, the whole video was real. And, really impressive!\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}